description: Traction AB engages in investment in listed and unlisted small and medium-sized companies. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 4 full-time employees.  Its activities are divided into three business areas: Customer relationships, providing customer-focused business models; Capital flows, offering the cost control; and Risk management, including share and reduce of risk factors. The firm invests in listed active holdings, such as BE Group, Drillcon, Duroc, Hifab Group, Nordic Camping & Resort, OEM International, PartnerTech, Softronic and SwitchCore, as well as in unlisted active entities, including Banking Automation, Modular Streams, Recco Holding and Sigicom. Furthermore, It is a parent of Ankarsrum Motors AB, Ankarsrum Kitchen AB, Ankarsrum Die Casting AB and Nilorngruppen AB.
naicsSubsector: Securities, Commodity Contracts, and Other Financial Investments and Related Activities
